  "keyFeatures": [
    "7 AI analyst agents (Technical, Fundamental, Options, News, Sentiment, Sector Rotation, Risk Manager) with bull-vs-bear debate and fund-manager synthesis",
    "Interactive REPL with 35+ commands for live quotes, analysis, and trade execution",
    "Quantitative strategy builder — describe in plain English, AI generates and backtests Python code",
    "Paper trading engine to simulate AI trade plans without real money",
    "Telegram bot with 14 commands and push price alerts",
    "OpenClaw HTTP skill server exposing 17 REST endpoints for agent integration",
    "Support for multiple AI providers: Gemini (free), Claude, OpenAI, Ollama, and any OpenAI-compatible endpoint",
    "Fyers broker integration for real-time NSE/BSE WebSocket data",
    "VaR/CVaR portfolio risk analysis, options Greeks, and pair trading",
    "Walk-forward backtesting, what-if simulator, and model drift detection"
  ],
